name: Evolve Enhanced Yield Bond Fund
longDescription: The ETF investing primarily in fixed income ETFs or fixed income securities issued in either the United States or Canada. The investment objective of the Evolve Fund is to provide Unitholders with attractive monthly income and longterm capital appreciation.
